{"tid":2156369,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出色裁判官系列：鄭念慈","createTime":"2020-08-14T11:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T04:46:17.000Z","uid":246828,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a2eb05e15ef3f0a81cb68ecfbf112d319e4b2be5","tid":2156369,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:37:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">呢單係831嘅首宗案件 會立壞先例</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第十三庭 <br />\n#鄭念慈裁判官<br />\n#裁決<br />\n#0831太子<br />\n<br />\n鍾(33)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n(2)無牌管有無線電通訊器材器具<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">(1)被控於2019年8月31日，於港鐵太子站內月台攜有攻擊性武器，即一個彈弓（即丫叉）、42粒螺絲帽，及一個能發出鐳射光束的裝置</span><br />\n(2) 被控於同日同地無牌管有2套無線電收發器<br />\n<br />\n裁決簡述：<br />\n案發時地事實無爭議點。港鐵太子站是眾所周知很繁忙的轉乘站之一，而晚上至十一時許有很多人也屬正常，被告亦知道自己身處有一定人流的鐵路站。<br />\n(1)彈弓及螺絲帽各自性質並無傷人價值，但二者在警員測試時配合起來，在<br />\n可射凹一塊5米外的一分厚層板；可見配合一起用時可對人構成傷害。<br />\n另外俗稱鐳射筆的裝置經專家證人檢測後，得出該裝置符合IEC 60825國際標準，屬第4級別亦是最危險級別之激光產品；雖然專家證人指商業或教學用途亦會用到鐳射筆，但無法解釋被告人當晚帶備以上物品。<br />\n(2)2套無線電收發器並無任何牌照。被告人在國內使用的工作用器具存放在香港使用的背囊亦不合理。<br />\n<br />\n在被告人帶上彈弓、螺絲帽、鐳射筆及適合使用於打鬥的保護裝備，有合理推測被告人有必然意圖對他人造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\n‼️兩項控罪罪名成立‼️<br />\n(1)很大機會判監（最高判監3年）<br />\n(2)罰款（最高罰款5萬）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">法庭就控罪(1)以12個月作量刑起點，判即時監禁12個月。控罪(2)罰款$5000，從$10000保釋金中扣除。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n證物P2-6充公、P7-16(衣物等物品)歸還被告、P19及25複印本予法庭存檔，正本還予控方、P20(木標靶)還予警方。<br />\n<br />\n‼️辯方律師最後申請刑期上訴期間保釋，法庭相信辯方將承諾儘快入紙，唯<span class=\"orange\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">保釋申請被拒</span></strong></span>。‼️"},{"pid":"99df6bfd095c995c8bdbd1a400d1264d6eb2e677","tid":2156369,"uid":246828,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c087efd44d614b11225e594370c5531b7006570","tid":2156369,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"裁判庭case係唔會成為案例"},{"pid":"b716c62b53f5601791f1616b96d44ed684ea5ed2","tid":2156369,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:44:55.000Z","msg":"紅官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba17b1237877d307ce686fbd66c6f6bc2e88629","tid":2156369,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9eb8b2424739c638dfd0fddefee795f6cb7278","tid":2156369,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28f032c4c98edd33432033fc01c49e220b62ac7","tid":2156369,"uid":237300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"見到個女人名，再見到張相原來係個男人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9664e7a95926bbe6f696b5076230ff76baf5d196","tid":2156369,"uid":329288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f28f032c4c98edd33432033fc01c49e220b62ac7","tid":2156369,"uid":237300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"見到個女人名，再見到張相原來係個男人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:52:22.000Z","msg":"我都以為係女狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b442557aa9e49305acaedbe74d423d1d091a0032","tid":2156369,"uid":27411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:55:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0649ae03e6f82c76a6f93fa62c2a5b0689fe777f","tid":2156369,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:56:53.000Z","msg":"狗官"},{"pid":"45330bf664fe4a3ba031b0ec6f24ece2fb8c023d","tid":2156369,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:57:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3f5cd7de1e9bea70c72b1e2f2558d9a704625a7","tid":2156369,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f28f032c4c98edd33432033fc01c49e220b62ac7","tid":2156369,"uid":237300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"見到個女人名，再見到張相原來係個男人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:01:51.000Z","msg":"一開始都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c80718938dfc22e860b308b3597261369d0526","tid":2156369,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a32d26bb22632d9838aba2e66e0240319b48b1c","tid":2156369,"uid":267537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"#九龍城裁判法院第七庭 <br />\n#鄭念慈裁判官<br />\n#裁決<br />\n<br />\n👥蕭,鄧,陳,韓,廖,陳,伍,方,蘇(15-34) #續審（#0803旺角 非法集結 管有攻擊性武器:一枝雷射筆D1）<br />\n<br />\n控罪一  參與非法集結<br />\nD1-D10 所有被告罪名成立<br />\n<br />\n所有被告即時還押<br />\n<br />\n所有控方警員證人證供被接納。即使有記事簿／書面口供與庭上不符，也認為<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">無心之失、語文程度不好、只屬於枝節</span></span>不至於影響證供可信性可靠性。"}]}